lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Jordan Spieth defeated Victor Dubuisson, 5 and 4, to earn his second win of the week in the World Golf Championships match-play event in Austin, Tex., on Thursday.

headline.main: Jordan Spieth Wins Again in Texas

snippet: Top-ranked Jordan Spieth defeated Victor Dubuisson, 5 and 4, to earn his second win of the week in the World Golf Championships match-play event in Austin, Tex., on Thursday.
abstract: Jordan Spieth and Jason Day chalk up second wins and clinch spots in round of 16 at World Golf Championships in Austin, Tex; other men's and women's golf scores noted.
